Package: GCSM
Title: Implements Generic Composite Similarity Measure
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Yadong",
           family = "Liu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "liuyadong828@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1283-3451"))
Description: Implements the generic composite similarity measure
    (GCSM), proposed in "A generic composite measure of similarity
    between geospatial variables" by Liu et al. (2020) <doi:10.1016/j.ecoinf.2020.101169>.
    Also provides implements of other composite measures, SSIM and CMSC.
